did.unittitle: Office and Professional Employees International Union, Local 23 records
did.abstract: Materials related to the Office and Professional Employees Inernational Union Local 23, Tacoma, Washington

bioghist.p: Office and Professional Employees Local 23 represented workers in the Tacoma area until the organization merged into OPEIU Local 8 of Seattle in 2015.

list.item: Series 1, Meeting Minutes and Financial Statements, 1937-2002
Series 2, Discontinued CBA files and Miscellaneous papers, 1936-1997
Series 4, Former Employer (Retail Store A-U) CBAs & Correspondence, 1937-2007
Series 6, Miscellaneous, photographs and newspaper clippings, 1936-2009

scopecontent.p: Records of the Tacoma local of the Office and Professional Employees International Union, including files on organizing campaigns, collective bargaining files and correspondence with employers; meeting minutes, newsletters, photographs & press clippings. Meeting minutes also include minutes from the Office Workers Local 20360 and OPEIU Local 132.

odd.p: Forms part of the Labor Archives of Washington.

accessrestrict.p: No restrictions on access. Records stored offsite; advance notice is required.

userestrict.p: Creator's copyrights transferred to the University of Washington Libraries Special Collections.

acqinfo.p: Donated by Libby Alejandro and Cindy Shu of OPEIU Local 8. Local 23 merged into Local 8 in June of 2018.
